Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've taken over Kaiba's Duel and Noah throws a barrage of attacks at me from his Spirit Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm careless,\N I'll be finished with one strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after I got an advantage with Cyber Pod's Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah's Deck Master Ability saved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the gap between Noah's Life Points and mine just got even more outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the odds were against me right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either way, I can't afford to lose this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"10000 Life Points VS 100!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've achieved a complete victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still very much alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! I just hit {\i1}Kuriboh{\i0}, of all things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! It's called Strength Increasing Medicine Super Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This launches when I take 2000 points of damage or greater from my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the damage is calculated, you increase your life by 4000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my Life rose to 4100 points before I took the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you made a major miscalculation in your prediction!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But while you are breathing a sigh of relief right {\i1}now{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've only prolonged your situation to witness an even {\i1}crueler{\i0} reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I laid damage on you in that battle hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, my Deck master Ability activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Life returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for an Instant Play Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebek's Blessing, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I am able to successfully lay damage to my opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the damage you lost is added to my Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me, Yamata Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This moment I'll activate the Effects of Element Fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}11000{\i0} Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the heck do you drain {\i1}that{\i0} much Life, OOH-AH~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba... Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bond with them\N isn't all that far away yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't afford to lose now of all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magnet Warrior Alpha in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacks of {\i1}that{\i0} level barely make me {\i1}flinch{\i0}, let alone {\i1}harm{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shall we begin the desperate countdown to the demise of you and your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotten scum!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I go to take a turn, one of your friends will vanish from your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! There's no point in trying to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our trust in Yugi won't change, regardless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest {\i1}assured{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awaiting the moment your little sister meets her end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a simple way to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is {\i1}defeat{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just {\i1}try{\i0} it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JUST TRY IT, YUGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Spirit Monster called Inaba White Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can directly attack the opposing player, regardless of whether they have Monsters on the field or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to me, White Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my Life Points increase once again due to my Deck Master Ability and the effects of Element Fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Life went up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Shizuka.\N Yugi's gonna win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a face-down card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Magnet Warrior Alpha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to Summon the Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because there is a black magician card resting in the Graveyard, her Attack Power increases by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the {\i1}matter{\i0}, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If {\i1}that's{\i0} the best you've got, you won't be saving your best friend's little sister anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to end my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desperate countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big... bro...ther...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIZUKA!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'll let you reflect on your weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon! Spirit Monster, Inaba White Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah! I've been waiting for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffin of Black Magic's Revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}Trap{\i0}, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffin of Black Magic's Revival activates the moment the opposing player Summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes the Monster you Summoned as an offering along with one of my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and revives a Black Magic User from my Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, Noah, I sacrifice your Monster, Inaba White Rabbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...along with a Monster of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I revive is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your Spirit Monster doesn't return to your hand, your Life Recovery Combo won't activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keh! I set a card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure that's a wise decision, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your field is completely empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you back to normal, no matter what I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, allow me to show you the true power of my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos - Black Magic Ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I sacrifice The Magnet Warrior - Magnet Warrior Valkyrion, an 8-Star Monster, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the wind that bears this ceremony, my honorable sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heir to chaos, born from the deep darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician of Black Chaos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whae...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Magician of Black Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three Warriors of Black Magic have descended!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All {\i1}three{\i0} Black Magicians?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have 7300\N Attack Points altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can turn this around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Warriors of Black Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take {\i1}this{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier of Confusion - Chaos Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Field is a Trap Card that activates when the opponent attacks with a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It selects the weakest Monster and forces it to fight the Monster with the highest Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, the Battle Phase is automatically ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my barrier will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician {\i1}Girl{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the Black Magician of Chaos's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician Girl...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Battle Phase has now been forced to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the damage you just received is added to my Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Life just went up even higher now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously though, that was {\i1}splendid{\i0}, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You possess both the judgment and the skill necessary to catch your enemies off guard the second they lose focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it, you and I have no reason to be enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you swear your loyalty to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save all your friends from hell this very instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, Seto and Mokuba are a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn them back to normal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning, both you and Seto existed to be enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why care what happens to Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no obligation to protect him, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}do{\i0} want your friends back to normal, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Kaiba is our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the feeling of siblings between those two are no different than they are for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that Otogi, Honda and Shizuka would have said the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}have{\i0} to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have to {\i1}win{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked for {\i1}your{\i0} piss-poor answer, commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah! You're really sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your knowledge may have advanced, but your heart has remained frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still nothing but a child who knows nothing about the world or the people that inhabit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, I shouldn't have expected commoners like yourself to understand my greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure someone chosen by victory will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I've chosen {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all you have to do\N is say you'll serve me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using your power to try and sway people's hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:13:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect people to accept you if you do things like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting really stupid, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stupid"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me {\i1}stupid{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you're such a {\i1}fool{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to do as you {\i1}wish{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then set a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since death is on the horizon for you, I'll be happy to tell you what this special card is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I'm about to set is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Groundbreaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me add a Spirit Monster lying in the Graveyard into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card I've brought back is obviously Inaba White Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've only got a measly 300 points of your Life remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can put an end to this Duel with a simple attack from the 700 Attack White Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granting me my perfect victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to end my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This match isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose this moment to activate the Trap Card, Groundbreaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I return Inaba White Rabbit to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Hand Obliteration!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must now send every card in your hand to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and draw the same amount of cards from your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician of Black Chaos, attack his Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Magic: Death Ultima!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Otohime's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She changes the Battle Position of one of the opponent's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Black Magician\N into Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Black Magician's Battle Phase is forced to a close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because a Spirit Monster on my side of the field has been destroyed, the Trap Card, Vessel of Illusions, can be activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It Special Summons a Spirit Token onto the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll Summon Otohime once again in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now, although...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it sure is getting a bit lonely now that the peanut gallery down there has been reduced to one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind sharing any last words you might have with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You must be feeling really angry at Yugi right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi will win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I'll believe in Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh~? Well if that's the case, I'll just end my turn without getting rid of you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain you'll feel differently the next time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I use {\i1}this{\i0} card, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Change of Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me control one of my opponent's Monsters until the end of the turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card I choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it feel? Losing the main card of your deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then sacrifice Black Magician and Otohime,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Summon the Spirit Monster holding the strongest Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hino-Kagu-Tsuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for a Spirit Equipment Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flaming Fist of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It increases the selected Monster's Attack Power by 200 points for one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hino-Kagu-Tsuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Extinction Fist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to both my Deck Master Ability and the damaging Effect of Flaming First, my Life Points increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I activate the Continuous Magic Card, Spiritual Energy Settle Machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then discard one card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this card is in play, my Spirit Monsters won't return to my hand at the End Phase of the turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my Life stands proudly at 10,000 and casts your pitiful 100 in shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you {\i1}still{\i0} believe you can turn this around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Yugi! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}fool{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu... gi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've lost them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay Yugi, this time for sure! I predict this is your final turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has Hino-kagu-tsuchi on the field, which has 3000 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't even {\b0}have{\b1} a Monster on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my hand is at zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I going to lose here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the friends that believed in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... it's not just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the room of my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me, it's true we still haven't found the Door of Truth in your room yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've made a new room instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is my new room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! So this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Room of Memories that you made after meeting all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'll ever have no one by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always here with you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're always cheering you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no way of winning this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man I acknowledge as my life-long rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me you're going to give up in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of our souls rest in the deck you're holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing short of the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got endless possibilities lying in this deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Possibilities that can turn the tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in our deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got... plenty of possibilities left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you {\i1}seriously{\i0} intending to fight in the condition you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, I still have things I need to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure from Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card forces both players to raw until they both hold six cards in their hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...are in you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here, Yugi-{\i0}san{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These cards hold all of their feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, let me say just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my prediction for the end of this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be taking another turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card, Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I'm reviving is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah, take mine and Mokuba's anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I won't let your hard work go in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Go, Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Toward our future!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for my second Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I polymerize the two Blue-Eyes in my hand with the Blue-Eyes I have on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, the strongest servant of Kaiba's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet another Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Hino-kagu-tsuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still not done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you, Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you won't be taking another turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion Cancel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Fusion Cancel automatically Summons three Blue-Eyes to the field, I still have a Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, this holds the wrath of my friends! And the bonds we share!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Kaiba and Mokuba's sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all built up in a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the strength of bonds!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it! Yugi won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still a monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, hurry up and give Honda back his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let us out of this Virtual Space already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You said none of us can leave this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, aren't you the one controlling this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Darkness of the Kaiba Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:23:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
